 <span data-ttu-id="c996b-161">이벤트의 시간에 오디오 상태를 가져오려면는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioStateChangedEventArgs.AudioState%2A> 속성은 연결 된 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioStateChangedEventArgs>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c996b-161">To get the audio state at the time of the event, use the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioStateChangedEventArgs.AudioState%2A> property of the associated <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioStateChangedEventArgs>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c996b-162">사용 하 여 인식기에서 인식기에 대 한 입력의 오디오 현재 상태를 가져오려면 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioState%2A> 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c996b-162">To get the current audio state of the input to the recognizer, use the recognizer's <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioState%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c996b-163">오디오 상태에 대 한 자세한 내용은 참조는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioState> 열거형입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c996b-163">For more information about audio state, see the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioState> enumeration.</span></span>  
  
